aboutpara: I am a Full Stack Developer with a background in UXD/UXR, education, and non-profit management. I am passionate about education for underrepresented people which drives me to create equitable and accessible designs. As a child of Deaf adults I have a special connection to the Deaf community which helps drive me to focus on equity and accessibility for all users.

resume.description: Well-versed with React, Python, Javascript. However, given 72 hours I can learn most languages and frameworks to a proficient level.

experiences.bullets: Built front-end features using React with a team of developers to solve user issues for classroom teachers

Analyzed data from clients using qualitative and quantitative methods to aid in discussions with software engineers for learning platforms. Worked with a Fintech startup using competitive analysis to optimize lead generation.
